            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-indigo-300 transition-colors">Words Ending in QI — Q-without-U survival guide</span>
          </a>
          <a href="/blog/best-words-for-triple-letter-squares/" class="flex items-center gap-2 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-900/20 transition-all group">
            <span class="text-indigo-400 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform shrink-0">→</span>
