      <div class="not-prose mt-10 p-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/20 to-blue-800/20 border border-blue-800 rounded-xl text-center">
        <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Practice Endgame Scenarios</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">Enter your remaining tiles and see what words are possible — plan your final moves with confidence.</p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-block px-5 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">Try the Word Finder →</a>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-400 mb-3">Related Articles</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/blog/best-vowel-heavy-words/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Best Vowel-Heavy Words for Scrabble</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/words-ending-in-qi/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Words Ending in QI</a></li>
